Color (BLACK/BLUE/RED): BLACK
Width: 4
Height: 5

Shape #2 data:
Rectangle or Circle (r/c)? c
Color (BLACK/BLUE/RED): RED
Radius: 3

SHAPE AREAS:
20,00
